<div id="deleteConfirmModal" class="delete-modal-overlay">
    <div class="delete-modal-box">
        <div class="delete-modal-icon">⚠</div>
        <div class="delete-modal-title">Confirmer la suppression</div>
        <div class="delete-modal-text">
            Êtes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer définitivement cet élément ?
        </div>

        <div class="delete-modal-actions">
            <button type="button" class="delete-cancel-btn" data-close-delete-modal>
                Annuler
            </button>
            <button type="button" id="confirmDeleteBtn" class="delete-confirm-btn">
                Supprimer
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>